Python Crash course book - Chapter 7 - Movie Ticket

Code:

age = input("Enter your age ")
while True:
  age = int(age)
  if age < 3:
    print("Ticket is free")
    break
  elif age < 13 :
    print("Your ticket price is $10")
    break
  else:
    print("Your ticket price is $12")
    break
    
Output:

Enter your age 10
Your ticket price is $10

Enter your age 15
Your ticket price is $12

Enter your age 1
Ticket is free

